                                    <p>
                                        <locus from="2r" to="2r" scheme="folios"/>, <locus from="13r" to="13r" scheme="folios"/>, penwork initial I over 8-9 lines in green with red flourishing. <locus from="32r" to="32r" scheme="folios"/>: penwork inital M in red over 6 lines. <locus from="145r" to="145r" scheme="folios"/>: inhabited initial C in red and green over 10 lines. Counter space filled with a ram and hound drawn in black ink, as well as vegetative ornamnets in red and green ink. Inital placed in red frame with flourishing and vegetative ornaments in green and black. <locus from="192r" to="192r" scheme="folios"/>: knotwork inital O over 10 lines, outlined in black ink, then filled with vegetative ornamnets in red and green. Inital placed in black and red frame with flourishing and vegtative ornaments in green and black. <locus from="213r" to="213r" scheme="folios"/>: vinestem inital V over 7 lines in black ink. This inital has not been filled in with colours. <locus from="2r" to="31v" scheme="folios"/>: plain initials over 3-4 lines in green with red flourishing or red with green flourishing. <locus from="2v" to="10v" scheme="folios"/>: plain initials in black with red flourishing over 2-3 lines. <locus from="32r" to="293v" scheme="folios"/>: plain Initials over 2-4 lined in green or red.</p>
